                            <div id="section2" class="mt-2 hidden">
                                <p class="text-gray-700">When responding to allegations and regulatory inquiries, our
                                    clients seek a mix of the right experience, technical capabilities, and footprint.
                                    Our forensic accountants check each box and have worked side-by-side with attorneys,
                                    corporate officers, and government officials to execute investigations involving
                                    allegations of financial statement fraud, layered instances of asset
                                    misappropriation, and cleverly orchestrated corruption. We understand how to manage
                                    the complexity of structured and unstructured data sets to make sense of what took
                                    place, how it happened, how extensive is the issue, and how can we remediate it.</p>
                            </div>
