                            </button>
                            <div id="section3" class="mt-2 hidden">
                                <p class="text-gray-700">We help clients investigate and respond to allegations of
                                    accounting and financial reporting (GAAP) fraud, as well as underlying model errors,
                                    breaches of fiduciary obligations, money laundering, embezzlement, white-collar
                                    crimes, and other acts of misconduct or non-compliance that may give rise to
                                    financial statement misstatements and create financial reporting fraud risks.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="border-b py-6">
                            <button
                                class="flex justify-between items-center w-full text-left text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-600"
